 Ariana Grande Announces Engagement To Dalton Gomez US singer and actress Ariana Grande has revealed she is engaged to her real estate agent boyfriend, Dalton Gomez. The star posted several photos on her Instagram page, showing a pearl and diamond ring on her left hand. “Forever n then some”, the caption said.  Grande, 27, has been dating Gomez, also in his twenties, for just under a year. The couple are currently living at Grande’s Los Angeles home, heeding California’s stay-at-home orders, reports say. View this post on Instagram A post shared by Ariana Grande (@arianagrande)